Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:11.36,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:20.99,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's been awhile...Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:22.38,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:22.38,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.33,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.33,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.56,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.56,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.27,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.27,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.38,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.38,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.33,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi mo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.33,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.96,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.96,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:43.40,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tanoshii uragiri ni atte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:43.40,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, betrayal can be pleasurable...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:46.70,J,,0000,0000,0000,,torawarenai atashi ga koko ni iru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:46.70,E,,0000,0000,0000,,But I stand right here - not giving in to temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:49.09,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tarinai tsukinai nandatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:49.09,E,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enough," "not enough," whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.19,J,,0000,0000,0000,,motto hizumasete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.19,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:55.05,J,,0000,0000,0000,,pataan kashita konna sekai ja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:55.05,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Living in this routine-laden world...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:58.07,J,,0000,0000,0000,,jibun ga dare nano ka wakaranakunaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:58.07,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...is enough to make you forget who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.26,J,,0000,0000,0000,,waku ni hamaritakunai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.26,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be stereotyped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:05.39,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kimetsukenaide yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:05.39,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't make assumptions about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.15,J,,0000,0000,0000,,michi naki michi wo yuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.15,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to blaze my own trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.55,J,,0000,0000,0000,,soko ni itatte matteitatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.55,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will ever be accomplished...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.44,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nani mo hajimaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.44,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you just stand around waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.18,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.18,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.35,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.35,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.95,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.95,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:26.85,J,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no omoidoori ni wa sasenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:26.85,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:27.86,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:27.86,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:30.12,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:30.12,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.09,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi wo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.09,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.63,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.63,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.27,J,,0000,0000,0000,,anata no moto ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.27,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm past the point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:41.32,J,,0000,0000,0000,,mou kaerenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:41.32,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot go back to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.25,J,,0000,0000,0000,,atashi wa atashirashiku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.25,E,,0000,0000,0000,,On my own terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:44.82,J,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:44.82,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:02.10,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of familiar\Nfaces here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:12.52,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we made it in\Ntime for the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.56,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.29,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Who...are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.25,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.00,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji...Hirako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.22,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji Hirako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:46.39,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Rojuro Ohtoribashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.35,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Rabu Aikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.23,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Hachigen Ushoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.31,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa Yadomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.05,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,I am assigning you five\Nas the investigation unit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.44,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,in charge of this\Nvanishing soul case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:31.38,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,101 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.33,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:57.23,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should be\Napologizing to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.50,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Because I chose you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:05.30,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,your friends ended up down there\Non the ground with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.75,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hirako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.35,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.90,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You're doing\Nthis to me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.30,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.99,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.63,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.60,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You were all wonderful\Ntest subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.81,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:07.83,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.24,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,What an...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.25,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,interesting guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.21,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:25.72,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you...come...you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.49,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant...Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.39,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.85,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.27,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.20,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.87,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find the members\Nof the investigation unit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:49.55,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,in charge of the vanishing soul\Ncase who were injured in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:52.28,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,and I was attempting\Nto rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.20,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Injured in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.12,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You call these "injuries"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.00,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.50,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Hollowfication.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.88,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,The vanishing soul case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.18,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Squad members disappearing\None after another as if erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.99,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.85,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Those were probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.15,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,"Hollowfication" experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.70,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Stand clear, Urahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.62,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number Eighty Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:41.63,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Hiryu Gekizoku Shinten Raiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.51,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo Number Eighty One...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.64,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Danku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.24,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:21.59,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,A lieutenant stopped my Kido using\NDanku without an incantation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:37.26,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I brought all eight of them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:42.23,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,And the new gigai prototype you\Nwere working on, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:45.94,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.09,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Get started on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.78,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment you heard about\Nthis incident from Hirako,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.68,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,you envisioned the\Nworst-case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.66,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,And you also came up with the\Nbest solution to counter that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.79,B2,JUDGE,0000,0000,0000,,I will pass sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.50,B2,JUDGE,0000,0000,0000,,The unfortunate captain\Nof Squad 5 along with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.80,B2,JUDGE,0000,0000,0000,,the other seven\Ncaptain-class members,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:15.06,B2,JUDGE,0000,0000,0000,,who became the victims of\Nyour heinous experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.81,B2,JUDGE,0000,0000,0000,,will be dealt with severely\Nas Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:28.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed the man\NI thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.98,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke did say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.54,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,"There were no miscalculations."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.49,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,That was the biggest\Nmiscalculation of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:47.42,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, everything turned\Nout in the worst possible way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.84,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we sure owe Kisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.76,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.53,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.62,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.48,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji Hirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:30.13,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you were hiding in\Nthe World of the Living...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.70,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since\Nwe last saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:42.24,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anybody in the Thirteen Court Guard\NSquads you guys want to say hello to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.10,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.34,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:47.40,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.97,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you\Nweren't talking to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.53,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking to everyone, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.70,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.99,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:03.24,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one in the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads I want to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.20,B2,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.46,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo isn't here. I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.06,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you\Ngoing, Lisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.34,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.13,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go say "hi" to the\NHead Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.26,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.70,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going\Nto play dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.64,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.78,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.88,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Look how beautiful you've become\Nsince the last time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.19,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.60,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how strong\NI've become!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.50,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:17.57,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.15,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.35,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.17,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to settle\Nyour grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.73,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Against Aizen, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.76,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything\Nagainst you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.36,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,One thing I am upset about is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.56,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that you placed an\Nincredibly strong barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.00,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,around this place to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.82,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't found this guy\Nkeeping watch outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:57.81,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,we would have been circling\Nthis area forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.50,B2,SASAKIBE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.53,B2,SASAKIBE,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't too sure whether\Nto let them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.69,B2,SASAKIBE,0000,0000,0000,,but considering the\Nsituation in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.83,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.29,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji Hirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:16.60,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Can we consider you\Nan ally for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:23.51,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.34,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.31,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're not your allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.23,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're Aizen's enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:45.20,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're also allies...of Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.25,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.50,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.93,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.17,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, but we can't waste\Nanymore time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.38,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is losing\Ntheir patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.83,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.72,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,He's ruining the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:21.64,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when he does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.86,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,There is meaning to\NWonderweiss's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.82,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.74,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What is he trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:43.71,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.80,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Are those all Gillians?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.47,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:28.97,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:32.76,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.72,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.64,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.56,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,You're all much too noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:52.03,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a party, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.66,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep it quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.58,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.55,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't roll these big\Nthings my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.41,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.75,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,Come near me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:50.17,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,And become enslaved\Nby my melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.38,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.64,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,They're incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.11,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,They're incredibly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.58,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.69,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:30.47,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotten pretty good at using\Nour Hollowfication, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.72,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.47,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.74,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.78,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.99,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.02,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to slice off everything\Nabove your left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:07.75,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't consider that a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.17,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Big talk coming from a small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:17.01,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,You must really hate the fact that you're\Ngoing to be killed by a small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.19,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Komamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.32,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to assist you,\Nmasked visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:39.37,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to help\Nshady looking guys like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:45.14,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, you look\Npretty shady yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:50.40,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You fought against those\NMenos Grande.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:54.82,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That alone is enough for\Nme to call you an ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.07,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided to fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.31,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I will not hear any objections,\Nmasked visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.46,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What a pushy fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.35,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good with guys like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.31,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Komamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:12.82,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to him go off like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.57,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,But he has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:37.84,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's no time to question\Nwhether you're a friend or foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:44.40,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really want to help\Nout you Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.52,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,But now's not the time\Nto be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.09,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:19:01.70,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,Strangers don't need a good\Nreason to team up in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:06.47,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy of your enemy\Nis your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.08,B2,LISA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good enough\Nreason to join forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.71,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.27,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.14,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.46,B2,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:32.06,B2,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,You can have that large one\Nover there. Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:35.27,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The big one...over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.03,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.24,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Kensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:45.20,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,Uniting against a common enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.66,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,is said to be one of\Nhumanity's bad habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.16,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:57.58,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bad habit, it's\Na survival instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:02.22,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it's at those times when spiritual\Nunions are at their most--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.56,B2,ROSE,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.32,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,We're done talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:12.81,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense and focus\Non the things at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.81,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look. He looks strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.78,B2,STARK,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to\Nremove your masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.42,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,We can only keep them\Non for three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.45,B2,LOVE,0000,0000,0000,,We're heroes, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.17,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.84,B2,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Super Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.69,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the exact opposite\Nof how it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:08.30,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined the day would come\Nwhere I would have to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.91,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,someone from your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.54,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:18.58,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,That someday we would\Ncross blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:24.30,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,And one of us would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.26,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:38.02,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Captain Komamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:43.53,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me join this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.80,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.84,J,,0000,0000,0000,,koe sae ushinattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.84,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I was stripped of my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:03.64,J,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa koko de utau darou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:03.64,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be here, singing my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:11.18,J,,0000,0000,0000,,koko kara hibike
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:11.18,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo out from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:19.98,J,,0000,0000,0000,,miminari ni kesareta seijaku no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:19.98,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The ringing in my ears stole the night's tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.92,J,,0000,0000,0000,,katachi nai mirai wo oikaketeta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.92,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I chased a future that doesn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:34.08,J,,0000,0000,0000,,sono te wa kuu wo tsukandekita kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:34.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet all I caught was nothing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:37.72,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to it! Listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.67,J,,0000,0000,0000,,deai ga tsumuideku merodi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.67,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The melody of the people we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.97,J,,0000,0000,0000,,oto ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.97,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...as I become sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:57.16,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa mada konna ni chiisa na kono koe ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:57.16,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my voice is still small and meager today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.69,J,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka wa tsuyoku hibiiteiku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.69,E,,0000,0000,0000,,One day it shall gloriously resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.32,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to it! Listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.16,J,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashiku yuriokosu merodi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.16,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet melody that'll awake\Nyou from your slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.60,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.91,J,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2800)}kimi ga omou kimi e
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.91,E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2800)}My song will reach the person you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:23.96,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,A horde of Menos is nothing\Nto us Visoreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.97,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,So, Shinji, how many\Ndid you defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:28.08,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how\Nmany I defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.34,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is how many\Nwe defeated together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:34.89,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from someone\Nwho hasn't defeated any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:36.68,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.69,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:45.44,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy Shinji really\Nbecame a baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.89,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:51.15,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I trimmed your hair while\Nyou were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:50.15,B2,HIYORI (OFF),0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ow, my stomach! My stomach\Nhurts from laughing too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:54.81,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:54.03,B2,HIYORI (OFF),0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're all shiny now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.29,B2,HIRAKO (OFF),0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how hard it was\Nto grow out my hair afterwards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:02.79,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:04.71,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that!